  EffectDiscription_ENG: "If you have a Digimon or Tamer with the [LIBERATOR]\_trait,
    you may ignore this card's color requirements.\n[Main] Reveal the top 3 cards
    of your deck. Add 1 card with the [LIBERATOR]\_trait among them to the hand.
    Return the rest to the bottom of the deck. Then, 1 of your Digimon may digivolve
    into a Digimon card in your hand with the digivolution cost reduced by 4."
